3281 Finished Sq. Ft. 3 Bedrooms, 3 Bath, Finished Basement, 2-Car Insulated Garage with 4' Extension, Covered Patio, Eat-In Kitchen Island, Spa Shower, California Style Walk In Closets in The Master, Main Floor Study, Gas Line at Range with 110V Outlet, Air Conditioner, Elevation B, Clerestory Window Package, Recipe Window Package, 8 foot Front Door, Front Yard Landscaping, Front Door WiFi Keypad, Recessed Light Package at Great Room, Kitchen Pendant Lights,  Whirlpool Stainless Steel Slide In Range, Dishwasher & Microwave. Ready October 2020.

Love to entertain? This is the PERFECT house for you. The Summit floor plan is new to the Oakwood Family & was designed with you in mind. Included in this home you will find 9' main floor ceilings, 8' front door, Quartz kitchen counters, Clerestory Window Package and much more! Your new home comes with the Oakwood Homes’ Guaranteed Energy Bill Program. This home is located in the award winning community of Reunion. The 2,500-acre community is located along 104th Avenue near E-470 in the northeast Denver Metro area. The high plains location offers great vistas of the Front Range and is just north of the Rocky Mountain Arsenal National Wildlife Refuge, south of Barr Lake State Park, and a convenient 15-minute drive to Denver International Airport (DIA). Easy access to E-470, I-76, and Highways 2 and 85 puts Reunion in a prime location to take advantage of downtown Denver and the Boulder corridor. Call our Inside Sales Team at 303.486.8915 to schedule an appointment.
